title: How To Recover Your Forgotten Facebook Password
creator: Brady Gavin
content: If you don’t use a password manager, those complex passwords can be pretty hard to remember. If you’ve forgotten your Facebook password, you can’t really recover that same password, but it’s easy enough to recover your account by resetting your password to something new.
